Title: Fix presentation of mirrored areas
Level: 1
Component: metrics
Compatible: compat
Edition: cee
Version: 1.5.0i1
Date: 1508413904
Class: fix

This werk fixes a bug in Check_MK metrics system:
When chosing "Mirrored Area" as a style in Graph Designer for multiple metrics, a "Mirrored Stacked" presentation got displayed instead.
